## Deployment

| Service | Platform | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Frontend | Vercel | Auto-deploys from `main` branch |
| Backend | Render | Web service, auto-deploys from `main` |
| Database | Supabase | Managed PostgreSQL |
| Files | AWS S3 | Resume storage |

